{"tid":982050,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"朗豪坊MONKI啲staff好閪","createTime":"2019-01-14T19:35:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T08:14:29.000Z","uid":204331,"like":18,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8fd16a6253d9846d65b977a30c0fc732167bc6e9","tid":982050,"uid":204331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T19:35:16.000Z","msg":"前日同frd去嗰到濕平啦 睇睇下衫聽到有人勁大聲講粗口又好多笑聲 一轉個頭睇 哇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成班staff三四個圍住fitting room岀面張枱到傾計 成班八婆咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  算啦我買衫姐就冇理啦 <br />\n之後我睇中咗件衫 但想要另一個size 就問啲staff啦 行去問兩個傾緊計嘅staff 兩個都話冇呀擺曬岀黎啦 但跟住隔離有個好啲嘅staff聽到就幫我入去揾 就真係有我個size<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌擺明偷懶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁之後我個frd又睇中咗條裙 但又揾唔到想要嘅size 佢又去問嗰兩個偷懶嘅staff 佢地又話冇 咁我就叫我個frd問嗰個好啲嘅staff 之後又真係揾到個size比佢<br />\n之後比錢嗰陣啲staff又一路講自己感情狀況一路收銀 完全當我冇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌我都未見過做sales做到好似呢班八婆咁閪 又柒又肥又懶又臭格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你要傾計嗰啲都冇所謂啦但都唔到連個客叫你揾個size都懶得serve啦 將心比心自己都唔想咁樣比人hea9啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0422715796b1de9fd484ce0847ce628cc8363913","tid":982050,"uid":175598,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T19:37:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c37653a15bc070fa6a9df3f2dbe57e1f1f95d811","tid":982050,"uid":129704,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T19:38:46.000Z","msg":"朗豪坊D staff係閪架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fafad0d2986aa84f7e8739dab222ec44414ddef","tid":982050,"uid":204331,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"0422715796b1de9fd484ce0847ce628cc8363913","tid":982050,"uid":175598,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T19:37:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T19